                            <comment id="16786771" author="elserj" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2019 13:36:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FWIW, I had pulled this change into a fork and ran into the same issue. I assumed it was an issue with my fork &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
